rComments: Dr. Halsall was very scattered and unorganized and that made things very difficult. Her criteria for assignments was unclear and sometimes she wouldn't post the criteria until the last minute. Might have been her first time teaching this class as she seemed really confused.

Literally all the driest content from APA 2140 was taken and put into this class. Found the course pretty disorganized and it was tough to see the purpose of most  things we were learning. This course in general is just a summary of a whole bunch of random studies which is really, really boring. The assignment made no sense and was graded tough.

Probably the worst teacher I have ever had. Lecture slides are very confusing, and she doesn't say anything during lecture to compliment them well. If you can manage to pay attention, you won't have a clue whats going on because she makes no sense.
